::DarkMouse::
Why the hell did I do that, she thought.
Before she went on the recon mission, she was going to get her mouth 
sterelized. She looked at Quickstrike and then at Megatron.

"Yes Megatron.  I agree with Quickstrike.  I can take Scorponoc and we can 
do the recon.  Let Quickstrike go do what he has to do."

She could barely stand being next to him.  She wanted to get as far away 
from Quickstrike as possable just as soon as possable.  If Megatron ordered 
them to work together, it would be a living hell for her.  She just wanted 
to get away from him, now if she could. More over, she wanted to find a hole 
and crawl into it.  What a fool she felt like. What made her do that? She 
felt like she'd throw up if she had to stand next to Quickstike one more 
second.

She walked over to Scorponoc. She said to him, "So you want to go and do 
some scouting around?"
